# Architecture — 일자리 Monorepo

## Layout

| Path | Role |
|------|------|
| `map/` | Flutter app (corporate, job seeker, admin, hiring) |
| `map/lib/features/<feature>/` | `domain/` · `data/` · `presentation/` |
| `map/lib/core/` | Shared: session, compliance, hiring, geo, address, config |
| `map/test/` | Widget + unit tests (mirror `lib/` paths) |
| `server/` | FastAPI — compliance, address, payments webhooks |
| `map/PUSH_PACKAGE_PRICING.md` | **요금 정책 SSOT** — 패키지·기본 플랜 |
| `map/PRODUCT_REQUIREMENTS.md` | PRD — §4 요금 |
| `map/PRODUCTION.md` | Runbook, dart-define, mock vs prod |

## Domain rules (do not drift)

### Push & packages (replaces partnership tiers)

- **Default plan**: 700m radius map pin (free), signup bonus 2 pushes, verification bonus 5 pushes, 1 base location.
- **Package product**: 5,000 KRW = 1 location slot + 1 push at **700m** from that base.
- **Bundles**: 10→45,000 / 30→120,000 / 100→350,000 KRW.
- **Wallet depletion**: signup bonus → verification bonus → package credits.
- **Job posting**: always free (no per-post fee).
- **Deprecated**: `premium_partnership_tier.dart`, partnership subscription, tier cards — migrate to `PushPackageCatalog` / `EmployerPushWallet`.

### Payments & entitlements

- Mock PG when keys missing (`env_config.dart`).
- **Paid**: push packages, cash wallet top-up — not job posting or successful hire (main app).
- **Contact/chat**: available on default plan (no tier gate).

### Commissions (partner builds only — default OFF)

- `ENABLE_HIRING_COMMISSION=false` on main app — no check-in success fee UI or billing.
- Code retained: `commission_calculator.dart`, `permanent_commission_calculator.dart` — enable per build for partner channels only.

### Address

- Mobile: Daum Postcode WebView (`daum_postcode_picker_page.dart`).
- Windows/desktop: QC manual entry when WebView unavailable (`workplace_address_qc.dart`).

## Conventions

- Flutter: feature-first folders; prefer `const` widgets; `AppColors`, `AppRoutes`.
- State: `AuthSession.instance` for current user/profile.
- New routes: register in `app_routes.dart` + navigator.
- Server: add routers under `server/app/`; keep secrets in `.env`, never commit.

## Before large changes

- Grep for existing pattern (e.g. tier cards, payment sections).
- Check tests under `map/test/features/<area>/`.
